Package edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model Description

Contains the DiscourseDB Core object model with the object relational mappings using Hibernate 4. Data access is provided by Spring Data repositories that can be found in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository. Note that the entity classes make use of Project Lombok"s @Data annotation to gererate Getter, Setters and constructors.
In order to make this work in eclipse, you need to run the lombok.jar on your developer machine to configure setup eclipse to support the generated code. More information about this can be found in the discoursedb-mode documentation on GitHub.
Author:
Oliver Ferschke
